<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-3682] ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException thrown by SkimpyOffsetMap.get() when full</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3682</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the SkimpyOffsetMap is full, a request for a key that is not in the map will throw an ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException as the number of internal attempts overflows after Integer.MAXINT&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12966165">KAFKA-3682</key>
