                            <comment id="15276559" author="githubbot" created="Mon, 9 May 2016 16:10:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user edoardocomar opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/1352&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/1352&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3682&quot; title=&quot;ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException thrown by SkimpyOffsetMap.get() when full&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-3682&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-3682&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException thrown by&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    SkimpyOffsetMap.get() when full&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Limited number of attempts to number of map slots after the internal&lt;br/&gt;
    positionOf() goes into linear search mode.&lt;br/&gt;
    Added unit test&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Co-developed with @mimaison&lt;/p&gt;

