&lt;p&gt;    This closes #1352&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;commit e27e9e2fee5922d7a2bb27fcac01a4ac18e8ca26&lt;br/&gt;
Author: edoardo &amp;lt;ecomar@uk.ibm.com&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Date:   2016-05-09T15:48:07Z&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3682&quot; title=&quot;ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException thrown by SkimpyOffsetMap.get() when full&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-3682&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-3682&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException thrown by&lt;br/&gt;
    SkimpyOffsetMap.get() when full&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Limited number of attempts to number of map slots after the internal&lt;br/&gt;
    positionOf() goes into linear search mode.&lt;br/&gt;
    Added unit test&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Co-developed with @mimaison&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;</comment>
